
# Apache Cloudstack Installatoin on Centos 7
 
# What all we will install with this roles
	1. First we will setup system pre-requisit ex: " Hostname, ip, DNS, IPtables, Selinux etc....."
	2. We will install mysql 5.6.21 version as recommned by the Cloudstack community.
	3. We will copy the files from file directory in required location.
	4. we will install cloudstack management server on management host.
	5. We will install NFS server for primary and secondary storage.
	6. Once installation is done, then will download system VM template on seconday storage
	7. We will deploy Zone,pods,cluster...etc...



Installation setps ----
	1. Clone the repository from github or download in ansible node
	2. 
